# Simplex (480KB block, no Coding)
#
# Scenario: EU proposer, US validator testnet
# Observed: ~400ms from proposal certificate to payload receipt

## Propose a block (480KB payload)
propose{0, size=491520}

## Multicast notarize (32B digest + 8B view)
wait{0, threshold=1}
broadcast{1, size=40}

## Multicast finalize after observing 2f+1 notarize (32B digest + 8B view)
wait{1, threshold=67%}
broadcast{2, size=40}

## Wait for 2f+1 finalize
wait{2, threshold=67%}
